          that systemd is being removed from <ulink url="http://en.opensuse.org/Portal:Tumbleweed">Tumbleweed</ulink> so that users won’t have a problem with it. That way it will allow
          developers to spend more time on working on it in order to have systemd ready for the
          upcoming 12.1 instead of chasing problems that are specific to Tumbleweed.</para>
        <para>Here is the <ulink url="http://lists.opensuse.org/opensuse-factory/2011-09/msg00877.html">e-mail</ulink>
          from Greg K.H. announcing the removal of systemd from Tumbleweed:<blockquote>
            <para>Due to a number of inter dependencies on packages that are not ready for
